{"word":"ἀποδεικτέος","slug":"ἀποδεικτέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀποδεικτέος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἀποδείκνυμι'><el>ἀποδείκνυμι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>one must prove</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> dupl. <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>one must make</i> one so and so, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}